{
  "stem": "21319.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one day, she saw me coming in, and going out from-- going to where the group of the people to meet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she reported me to this Lithuanian police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And when I came out from Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Bagdonas house, walking back to meet the group, the working group, to go back to the ghetto, two policeman, Lithuanian, they were in charge, picked me up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they took me to the police station in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was the headquarters there also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't know why they did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In ghetto, you're not supposed to get-- do you have a [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't have no [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the men were sitting-- there was a man sitting in the room, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He took me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I told them that I worked for Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bagdonas.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he didn't believe me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you lie.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you're going to go to Lukiskes, which the people were sent to Ponary to death.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I ask him a favor, if you could get in touch with Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bagdonas.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, no, Jew, you a Jew, so and so, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I waited from the hole that the police had to pick me to take me to Ponary, to Lukiskes Ponary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the girl from the ghetto, from [NON-ENGLISH], a Jewish girl used to clean their place there, what is meant to be alive, huh?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She saw me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she knew who I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, because she probably knew me from [NON-ENGLISH], where I used to come and maybe visit my sister or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she had mentioned my sister's name, probably.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she-- and one, she ran from that place.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
